privateinfo.privatecomment: * Contains components of expansions: ** Charter Companies Mini-Expansion (2018) ** Endeavor: Age of Expansion (2020) ** Seize Your Fate Mini-Expansion (2020) ** Dominium Micro-expansion (2020) * Retail and replaced components in Endeavor: Age of Expansion box

item.comment: Very nice looking (I've got the Commodore edition ;-)) game, with straightforward rules, which are not too heavy to understand that can be played in a fast pace as actions quickly follow after one other. Game play takes less than 2 hours, which makes it a game easily taken out the shelves. The exploits can make your strategy change every game, although you can play as well without them.
